title: Judwaa 2 2017 HINDI [DDR] FULL-EVO
description:
Judwaa 2 2017
Action, Comedy, Drama 

Prem and Raja are twin brothers who are seperated at birth but are uniquely connected to eachother via their reflexes. They 

reunite as adults and set out to take down the underground smuggling world.
Director: David Dhawan
Writers: Yunus Sajawal (screenplay), Farhad Samji (dialogue) 
Stars: Salman Khan, Anupam Kher, Jacqueline Fernandez
